{"type": "article", "id": 8003, "title": "USB 充电器", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-01T07:23:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052346125rjk9xSO2duwve7o.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tJasper Morrison 设计的这一款充电器意在解决桌面线材凌乱和器材同时充电的问题。目前人们普遍习惯拿 USB 线充电，但是许多电脑的 USB 接口数量有限，这时 UC 01 便可以派上用场了。看起上虽然有点笨笨的，但轻便的设计使得它十分便于携带，并排的插口也让线材看上去不那么凌乱不堪。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234609C0j5ymxW2Ug4oLB1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234609Uu1yDTqrLlsWgZA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234610mHsYFfilxkehSqTM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.64669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234610maThyUzu0XKS1Fjo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73471883\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234611KkzwmNFZdI2qlCV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234611yKfhEpgowOsbrSX8.jpg\" alt=\"\" styl